flowchart TD
    Conn[Incoming Connection] --> AuthN{1. Connection AuthN}
    
    AuthN -->|Plaintext / Permissive| DenyOrAllow{Is Strict mTLS enforced?}
    DenyOrAllow -->|Yes| Drop[Drop Connection (mTLS Required)]
    DenyOrAllow -->|No| ReqAuth{2. Request AuthN}

    AuthN -->|mTLS Confirmed| ReqAuth
    
    ReqAuth -->|Extract JWT Claims| AuthZ{3. AuthZ Policy}
    ReqAuth -->|No JWT / Optional| AuthZ
    
    AuthZ -->|Matches Rules: Source/Path/Action| Allow[Allow Request to App Container]
    AuthZ -->|No Match / Denied| Reject[Reject Request: 403 Forbidden]

    style Conn fill:#f8fafc,stroke:#cbd5e1,color:#0f172a
    style AuthN fill:#e2e8f0,stroke:#94a3b8,color:#0f172a
    style ReqAuth fill:#e2e8f0,stroke:#94a3b8,color:#0f172a
    style AuthZ fill:#e2e8f0,stroke:#94a3b8,color:#0f172a
    style Drop fill:#ef4444,stroke:#dc2626,color:#fff
    style Reject fill:#ef4444,stroke:#dc2626,color:#fff
    style Allow fill:#10b981,stroke:#047857,color:#fff
